# wurl

Wurl is a simple URL parsing library that provides Pathlib-like usage to URLs in Python:

```python
>>>> wu = Wurl("https://wordbrew.io")
>>>> wu / "about" / "index.html"
https://wordbrew.io/about/index.html

```

